---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../../lib/constants';
---
<BaseLayout title="Imprint" description="Legal notice pursuant to § 25 Austrian Media Act.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Imprint</h1>

    <div class="prose mt-10">
      <p>Information obligation according to § 25 Mediengesetz (Austrian Media Act).</p>

      <h2>Media owner and publisher</h2>
      <p>
        Ing. Michael Linder, MSc<br />
        Nötsch im Gailtal, Carinthia, Austria<br />
        Email: <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Editorial direction</h2>
      <p>
        Personal website and blog. All content reflects the author's own views. There is no editorial affiliation with any company or organisation.
      </p>

      <h2>Professional activity</h2>
      <p>
        Freelancing via <a href="https://strali.solutions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Strali Solutions e.U.</a> (FN 474736t, VAT ATU72580414).
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
